      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 87: Appending `/usr/lib/$(HOST)/pkgconfig` and `/usr/share/pkgconfig` to `PKG_CONFIG_PATH` for native contrib builds allows host packages to satisfy contrib dependency checks. That weakens reproducibility and can silently mix system libraries with the contrib prefix, especially after raising `opendht` to `\u003e\u003d 4.0.0`. Prefer keeping contrib resolution constrained to `$(PREFIX)` and pass host pkg-config paths explicitly only for the specific package that requires them.",
